The Green Mile;;94;;78;;R;;Paul Edgecomb (Tom Hanks) walked the mile with a variety of cons. He had never encountered someone like John Coffey (Michael Clarke Duncan), a massive black man convicted of brutally killing a pair of young sisters. Coffey had the size and strength to kill anyone, but not the demeanor. Beyond his simple, naive nature and a deathly fear of the dark, Coffey seemed to possess a prodigious, supernatural gift. Paul began to question whether Coffey was truly guilty of murdering the two girls.;;Fantasy,Drama;;Frank Darabont;;1999;;Tom Hanks,David Morse,Michael Clarke Duncan,Bonnie Hunt,James Cromwell,Michael Jeter,Graham Greene,Doug Hutchison,Sam Rockwell,Barry Pepper,Jeffrey DeMunn,Patricia Clarkson,Harry Dean Stanton,Dabbs Greer,Eve Brent,William Sadler,Gary Sinise;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/green_mile